{{Infobox ethnic group
|group    = Iranun / Ilanun people<br><small>''Orang Iranun / Ilanun''</small><br><small>''Mga Iranun / Ilanun''</small>
|image    = [[File:The Iranun (Ilanun) Moro 'pirate'.jpg|250px]]
