{{Expand Czech|topic=culture|date=August 2010|Marketa Lazarová (kniha)}}
'''''Marketa Lazarová''''' is a [[Czech language|Czech]] novel, written by [[Vladislav Vančura]]. It was first published in 1931. The novel was adapted into the acclaimed 1967 film ''[[Marketa Lazarová]]''.

==English translations==
*''Marketa Lazarová'', translated from the Czech by Carleton Bulkin, Prague, Twisted Spoon Press, 2016, {{ISBN|9788086264431}}

